Invocation Name: winds aloft
des: This skill was designed for free flight pilots and tells the winds above Denver, Colorado at 9k, 12k, and 18k feet. Data is based on Aviation Weather from the National Weather Service.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
